OL,3,CJersey's tenancy deposit scheme renewed
OL,5,FJersey's tenancy deposit scheme has
OL,6,Fbeen renewed for a further three years.
OL,8,FThe initiative, established to
OL,9,Fsafeguard tenants' deposits at the end
OL,10,Fof their tenancy, makes it a legal
OL,11,Fobligation for landlords to properly
OL,12,Fprotect a deposit.
OL,14,FFailure to comply may result in
OL,15,Fprosecution.
OL,17,FHousing Minister, Deputy Sam Mezec
OL,18,Fsays, "Any landlord who does take a
OL,19,Fdeposit from their tenant must use
OL,20,Fthis scheme - it is actually a
OL,21,Fcriminal offence not to comply.
