OL,5,F"The worst outcome if a landlord
OL,6,Fdoesn't comply is prosecution, because
OL,7,Fit is an offence not to use this
OL,8,Fscheme."
OL,10,FThe decision follows the States
OL,11,FAssembly's approval of updates to the
OL,12,FResidential Tenancy Law in September
OL,13,F2025 and the introduction of a
OL,14,Flandlord licensing scheme in May 2024.
OL,16,FSince the Mydeposits scheme was
OL,17,Fintroduced in November 2015, nearly
OL,18,F10,000 islanders' deposits have been
OL,19,Fsafeguarded, worth around #15 million.
