OL,3,CJersey's tenancy deposit scheme renewed
OL,5,FIt means deposits are held securely
OL,6,Ffor the length of a tenancy, with
OL,7,Finterest from them used to fund the
OL,8,Fscheme.
OL,10,FDeputy Mezec says it is important
OL,11,Ftenants know if their landlords have
OL,12,Fsigned up.
OL,14,FHe explains: "Tenants should be given
OL,15,Fa reference number by their landlord.
OL,16,FIf they don't hear anything, they can
OL,17,Fgo to Mydeposits and ask if they have
OL,18,Fyou on file. That's the easiest way to
OL,19,Ffind out.
