OL,5,F"The worst outcome if a landlord
OL,6,Fdoesn't comply is prosecution, because
OL,7,Fit is an offence not to use this
OL,8,Fscheme, and all sorts of problems can
OL,9,Farise if the scheme isn't being used
OL,10,Fproperly by both parties."
OL,12,FHe adds that the protection service
OL,13,Falso provides a free, impartial
OL,14,Fdispute resolution service, aiming to
OL,15,Fensure disagreements over deposits are
OL,16,Fresolved fairly and at no cost to
OL,17,Feither party, while also avoiding the
OL,18,FPetty Debts Court.
