OL,3,CJersey's tenancy deposit scheme renewed
OL,5,FEddie Hooker, Founder and CEO of
OL,6,FMydeposits, says: "As we enter this
OL,7,Ffurther term, we'll focus on making
OL,8,Fdeposit protection even easier to
OL,9,Funderstand and access, raising
OL,10,Fawareness of renters' rights and
OL,11,Fresponsibilities, and supporting
OL,12,Flandlords and letting agents to comply
OL,13,Fwith Jersey's standards."
OL,15,FThis initiative forms part of the
OL,16,FCouncil of Ministers' strategic
OL,17,Fpriorities to improve the experience
OL,18,Fof renters, deliver a new Residential
OL,19,FTenancy Law, and review the social
OL,20,Frents policy.
